<page api="xb">
    <shortlink>api layout delete function</shortlink>
   <topic>LAYOUT_DELETE Function</topic>
     <description>Deletes a Form, Browse, Label, Letter, or Report Layout </description>
   <syntax>L layout_delete(C layout_name ,C layout_type [,L flagRefreshControlPanel ])</syntax>
   <arguments>
     <argument>
         <name>layout_name</name>
         <description>The name of a form, browse, label, letter, or report layout.</description>
     </argument>
     <argument>
         <name>layout_type</name>
         <description>One of the following values: "Form", "Browse", "Label", "Letter", "Report".</description>
     </argument>
     <argument>
         <name>flagRefreshControlPanel</name>
         <description>Logical</description>
     </argument>
   </arguments>
 
   <discussion>
LAYOUT_DELETE() deletes the named layout. The function displays an error message if there is no layout of the specified name and type, or if either field has a NULL value.

   </discussion>
   <example><![CDATA[layout_delete("Category_Form", "Form")
layout_delete("Method Browse", "Browse")]]></example>
   <limitations>Desktop applications only.</limitations>
